{"tid":2447684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美太空司令部擬與日本加強合作 強化太空戰力","createTime":"2021-03-15T11:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T11:13:08.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"757735f2444e04a0fc1ddd561c887548fc6008ff","tid":2447684,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:03:06.000Z","msg":"美太空司令部擬與日本加強合作 強化太空戰力<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%8F%B8%E4%BB%A4%E9%83%A8%E6%93%AC%E8%88%87%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E5%BC%B7%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%88%B0%E5%8A%9B-160000235.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%258F%25B8%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%258A%259B-160000235.html&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=9786872e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%8F%B8%E4%BB%A4%E9%83%A8%E6%93%AC%E8%88%87%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E5%BC%B7%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%88%B0%E5%8A%9B-160000235.html</a><br />\n<br />\n「Breaking Defense」12日報導，美國太空司令部（SPACECOM）宣布將與日本強化正式合作關係，雙方已就合作備忘錄內容展開協商，代表日本有望加入加州范登堡太空基地內的跨國太空合作辦公室，與美、德、法、英等國家，共同協調太空政策與聯合戰術等，強化跨國太空合作。<br />\n<br />\n美國太空軍軍令部長雷蒙上將2月赴國會作證時，就已透露日本將加入太空司令部跨國合作行列，他強調，跨國太空合作辦公室旨在讓來自合作國家的聯絡官，共同研擬太空相關政策，以及太空作戰之聯合戰術、技術及程序等，以強化太空戰力。除了日本外，目前也正在推動南韓與義大利加入。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">SPACECOM司令狄金森上將就任以來，積極推動太空多邊合作關係，尤其是在印太區域，藉此嚇阻中共逐漸崛起的太空力量。太空軍參謀主任阿瑪格諾中將也說，太空軍視聯盟為美軍成功關鍵，「美國絕不單打獨鬥」。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n美國太空軍去年12月宣布，與日本宇宙航空研究開發機構（JAXA）國家太空政策辦公室簽署備忘錄，由太空軍「太空暨飛彈系統中心」（SMC）打造的光學感測器，預計在2023與2024年利用日本衛星，自日本種子島太空中心發射升空。美軍新聞稿並指出，強化太空覺知能力將是美日太空合作的第一步，將以此備忘錄為基礎，進一步深化合作。"},{"pid":"b1c2474731a80c424d9f024362131fdb2451dce5","tid":2447684,"uid":45456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"整高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"11d2fd27d5b1c223a824c201c9db3cf88372e91d","tid":2447684,"uid":268621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:09:29.000Z","msg":"一開打，即時射晒啲北斗衛星，變成太空垃圾，有核彈都只能自爆。"},{"pid":"746910726de69556aa8caba04eae93f16cac8246","tid":2447684,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1c2474731a80c424d9f024362131fdb2451dce5","tid":2447684,"uid":45456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"整高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"軌道戰機"},{"pid":"a59b4a118f0a1be8c71ab848f2b528e4d6c408cb","tid":2447684,"uid":387466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:10:20.000Z","msg":"幾時起side 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03dc76bf7cf6bd04508d2586229ba88e9a5f4eee","tid":2447684,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5xOinsh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5xOinsh.jpg&h=f65cc109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太空戰士"}]}